        " عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ : \"مَنْ غَسَلَ يَدَهُ قَبْلَ اَلطَّعَامِ وَ بَعْدَهُ عَاشَ فِي سَعَةٍ وَ عُوفِيَ مِنْ بَلْوَى فِي جَسَدِهِ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.4265 - Imam (as) said: \"Whoever washes his hands before and after eating will live in ease and will be protected from afflictions in his body.\""
